i dont know what to do... everything seems just so confusing! i feel like im completely lost and i dont know why. maybe im just stressed out becuase schools almost over, thank god, becuase if its not that, i dont now what it is. i start work tomorrow morning! finally... money! haha 11-4 saturdays and 4-10 tuesdays... but i wont get to work with my brother :( yet... i get to rain with the other manager, who im already friends with cause of my bro. his name is arbin... ya weird i know, but hes nice. then i have.. mmmmm right, nothing to do for the rest of the weekend. i wanted to hang out with a friend but he has something to do so that idea wont do me any good! oh well... ill think of something.
    lately me and a girl on my squad have been thinking about summer and next season... ooooh were already planning! this summer were going to "flip camps"... aka tumbling... haha we wanna get our tumbling better for next season. weve also been thinking about who our coach is gonna be.  the coach weve had for the past 2 years said she only coach if nikkis mom helped her out because she wants to see some ofher sons fotoballs games this year. shes probably gonna end up doing it, which will be cool cause shes an AMAZING coach and nikkis mom is great too. was also doesnt have football... but next year will be our first season with a team... and theyre starting out JV. the catch is... they want the cheerleaders to cheer for them, obviously... BUT BUT BUT... varsity cheerleaders for jv football isnt so fun... and they expect us to do it in our uniforms, which our coach disagreed too. she said wed only cheer if they got us warm-ups, and the ones we wanted. so well see how THAT goes... but if you have any advice for suggestions for season please let me know!
    if your from the new england area and you know of tumbling camps/clinics that go on during the summer... itd be great if you could let me know! thanks everyone!

<3 cara :)

im doing this poem for an english assingment... i thought it was amazing, so lemme know what you think please! 

     If You Forget Me
       Pablo Neruda

I want you to know
one thing.

You know how this is:
if I look
at the crystal moon, at the red branch
of the slow autumn at my window,
if I tough
near the fire
the impalable ash
or the wrinkled body of the log,
everything carries me to you,
as if everything that exists,
aromas, light, metals,
were little boats
that sail
toward those isles of yours that wait for me.

Well, now,
if little by little you stop loving me
I shall stop loving you little by little.

If suddenly
you forget me
do now look for me,
for I shall already have forgotten you.

If you think it long and mad, 
the wind of banners
that masses through my life, and you decide
to leave me at the shore
of the heart where I have roots,
remember
that on that day,
at that hour,
I shall lift my arms
and my roots will set off
to seek another land.

But
if each day,
each hour,
you feel tha tyou are destined for me,
with implacable sweetness,
if each day a flower
climbs up to your lips to seek me,
ah my love, ah my own,
in me all that fire is repeated,
in me nothing is extinguished or forgotten,
my love feeds on your love, beloved,
and as lond as you life it will be in your arms
without leavig mine.

oops... way for me to forget about livejournals huh? well the only time i can actually update this thing is english class or at friends houses, cause my computer has compu-aids! woohoo... soooooooooo everythings been good lately. i guess... probably not. people are gay and continue to be gay, which is totally cool! aaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaah NOT. but aside from stupid people, things are pretty good i guess. friends are all good. oh ya! i go tmy permit a few weeks ago and im in drivers-ed, which suprisingly, isnt boring cause my teacher is a fucking psyco. softball could DEFINATLY be better than it is... we had a game yesterday and didnt do anything but make errors which sucked... so we lost to a bad team... not fun at all. but i have a few new friends from hyde school... their cool, but leaving on the 29th :'( for 3 months! ah! wellllllllllllllll ill still get to talk to them on the internet and what not. well i have to get back to writing my paper. soooooooooo until later? lets hope so

wow... its been a few days... im in vermont for the weekend... gotta love those long weekends! haha ah and brit and joe just got here... that means I GET FOOD! woop! i love this... soooooooooo more later? yesssss MOST definatly

confused... i dont even know what to do anymore, and it sucks so bad. i like *him* a lot... and from what he says he likes me... but so does his best friend, which causes so much shit to happen. im stuck in the middle of all of it too. i dont want *him* to walk away from this, from me... you know? i want him to stay a while... i really want him to stay a while. and with his best friend... oooooh boy, thats a whole nother story. heres my issue in a nutshell... i like *him* a lot and he likes me. we talk and hang out when we get the chance and its great, i love it! but his best friend likes me and he confuses the hell outta me. last night he told me "i know you like him but what if you end up not liking me"... think about it, it made no sense to me... but thats just an opinion. i wish everything would get figured out... this situation is shitay...
  what else is new... softball is started :) lovin it lovin it! i got my number this year, thank god! 3 bitches! woop! hahha softball makes me happy. we have a good team this year, and im anxious to see our outcome. im the starting catcher for the jv team, by the way. its cool... i have fun so its allllll gravy. but i must say... i miss cheerleading!!!! :'( A LOT
  talkin to jon again... ya... i dont even know what to say about him... its been a while... hes still the same little shit head as he was before... thats right... i said THE SAME... hes jon... woohoo *twirls finger in air* just kidding jon... im not gonna even touch the subject of other people... but jon... hes a loser and you should all hate him :)
  more later... im in desperate need of food, clean clothes, and a shower... maybe a good cry too :/

wow do people make me angry... YOU GOT CAUGHT GET OVER IT! got why do you piss me off so much... and then other people need to make up their minds and be ONE person with ONE mind... not ONE person with like 789577539847 minds... GOD I HATE SOME PEOPLE... tonight i get to stay with my big ss so im happy and i think i get to see *him* :D im excited... but class is over... more later... 

p.s. f yooooouuuuuu 

RIP mitch :'(

ITS MY 16TH BIRTHDAY TODAY! oooooh i am so happy... this has been a good day... last night my friend kept me on the phone until 1205 just so he could be the first one to say happy birthday to me :) hes great!! katie showed up at my house this morning with 10 balloons... made me carry one around school, then my mom sent me 16 pink roses and a balloon at school... oh ya... i was just oh so thrilled to get to carry those around all day! hahaha

   winter awards are tonight! :'( that means cheerleading is really over! it sucks! thats my favorite and best sport that i do... and now i gotta wait till august to start up again... unless i find a good all-star team... any suggestion? im up for some... 

well ummmm im in english class... sooooo ill probably write more later tonight! love you alllllll!
                     <3 Cara

wow... its been a while! i seem to have a slight problem with keeping on my toes when it comes to updating this thing :/ sorry guys... anywho... yesterday was probably one of the worst days of my life... one of my close friends moved to Arrizona at 5 and im probably never gonna see him again. ive been crying pretty much since i got home from school at 3, and if i wasnt crying, i was holding it in with everything i have. i hate her... her referring to the bitch that took him from everyone he knows and ruined his life. because of her i lost a great friend that i probably will never speak to or see again unless by some miracle chance were in florida at the same time... which kinda sucks :'( but looking on the bright side of things... i talked to him today... a few times actually because his cell phone hates me! i swear it was every like, 8 minutes it would disconnect. he was being a funny kid! haha he told me that i wasnt allowed to go to his baseball games with him because then i would never need sex cause i would orgasm over the guys that were on the field... i couldnt help but laugh hysterically! and it turns out that he spent most of the night at a party about 2 seconds from my friends house... let me tell you, i found that out and i wanted to scream! ummm i dont think i was supposed to fall for him like i did... but, its ok because i really do like him... hes great:) so tonight i watched passion of the christ and it fucking creeped me out SO BAD... it wasnt scary, but some parts in that movie really can creep you our a little... theni watched the exorcist and now im watching the exorcist the beginning... hmmmm i love it. im big on scary movies... however i do prefer to watch them with guys! haha havent talked to the baby since ummm yesterday? what is there even to say about him anymore... hes my love and we fight like its our fucking job... ya its just fun shit! jason is being a lil weird lately too... but i dont even know what to do anymore... with any of them... im conflustered and it sucks. i hate not knowing what to do... but jason knows. we determined that i dont need to tell jason what to do anymore because he already knows, me saying it just proves him right, so i dont bother anymore... oooh yup and my birthdays TUESDAY! woohoo!!! im excited... sweet 16 bitches... it makes me happy... i love it... 
  cheerleading ended on sunday:'( i was SO sad... those are my 2 favorite seasons out of the school year... and now i gotta wait till august or september to start unless i join an all-star team, which i am definalty considering.  does anyone have any suggestions as to some good all-star teams in CT? if you do please let me know... i would very much appreciate... even though softballs starting im still looking... maybe ill pull 2 cheering teams next year. yup softball starts monday, the day before my birthday! woohoo... no i really am looking forward to it but then again im kinda not... its a LOT of hard work but im totally up for it.
   oh well... enough for now... movie time... then probably bed... sleeping till 12 and calling him at 1201 cause thats when he gets out of school :D yay! ta-ta for now my loves...
                                      *(.Cara.)*
3.18... i will remember you... will you remembe me... dont let your life pass you by... i will love you until forever, until the stars fall from the sky :'(

its been a few days, hasnt it?! haha wow... im in such a great mood... but at the same time in so upset about everything... great because ive had a great few nights. last night at practice Nikki finally twist craddled! and they were SO gorgeous... were all so proud of her. its taken her 4 years to get over her fear of it and now that she can do it she wont stop! shes like the energizer bunny on speed! hahaha wow and jon... what to say about him... hes great :) i havent seen him since tuesday... valentines day is 1 month... im excited, but it just feels so weird... i dunno... i being retarded and a half again :/ oh well... and ive been getting along with jason lately! im so happy about it... we were fighting for the longest time, well more like i had major issues with him for my reasons... but now everything is better. ive been talking to him a lot since this past weekend. ah yes and then theres the baby.. aka jonthan. for those of you who think i hate him... I DONT! hes my best friend and i love him! lol im just not very happy with his umm "girlfriend"... ya i liked her at first but i lost ALL respect for her after last night. ya i bitched her out pretty bad... then she pulled the change the subject thing... whatever i just dislike her now... but last night i was talkig to him online and i was listening to my launch-cast on yahoo and "All My Life" by Kc and jojo came on.. for the first time ever i lied to him... he asked what song it was and i told him that it was a song from me and a friend... but it wasnt... it made me cry cause thats the song that he told me was perfect for how he felt about me when we were dating. i dont even wanna say whats on my mind right now... everything is just... i dunno... there arent words for it... then theres jackie. i havent talked to her in over a week and yesterday she calls me after school and i was like oh? then i had to go to cheerleading and i havent talked to her since... im still just all fed up or whatever with what happened between us... i dont think anyone knows what im talking baout, but thats OK! lol soooooooo i guess other than this... my life is just dandy... slightly rough around the edges... but good... ill write more later maybe... its not like i have anything else do to! hahaha well maybe ill get a hair cut.. that would be nice :D lol so long for now...
              <3 always

            *(*.Cara.*)*

Absolutly Amazing! oooooooooooh man this has been one fucken odd week... oh yes! i have to update everyone... i have a new boyfriend :) and coinsidently his name is jon... hes AMAZING... hes almost 17 and he goes do a different school than me... but wow... just thinking baout him makes me speechless... thats how great it is! hes like a best friend and a boyfriend all packed into one... i just love him to death! and an update on the other jon (now refered to as the baby)... he has a new girlfriend! im so excited for him... haha hes all happy and shit and im happy so were both good... for the first time in a while were both happy... kinda weird at the same time though if you know what i mean... lol buuuuuuuutttttttttt i dunno... i just feel like smiling all the time right now... even though im tired as hell... OH YA! another update... i dyed my hair reddish-brown... its real cute... but it will definalty take some getting used to! other than all the good stuff thats happening... this week has been... well... interesting... cheerleading is rough, i have a broken toe and we have competition on saturday so that will be loads of fun considering i have to do a standing back-hand-spring and a round off back-hand-spring... and we had one last saturday and we got 4th so that was cool... we did good, but could have been better. i kinda wanna shoot myself in the face... cause people are fucking gay and need to get over shit... i have stress coming out my fucking nose... its rediculous... and one of my sanity's is in aruba without me! hahaha my friend came to visit for a week... so i was excited to see him too... but i dunno... everythings just kinda... blah ifyou know what i mean... but i think im gonna go to bed... i have school in the morning and i get to see jon tomorrow so i need beauty sleep! haha wow and i just realized that its fucking snowing... AGAIN... damn snow... but anywho... ill write more eventually..
                          <3 cara

has anyone ever had that feeling like you dont know whats going on in your head... like maybe you should invest in some wonderful filing cabinets to straighten it all out?? yup... sucks doesnt it? well i can tell you one thing... i hate it and not knowing whats going around me is making me feel like shit... ive had my moments where im not happy before... but now im in love and not happy. this is a new one... and i dont get it... i dont get anything anymore... i love him, i really do! but im not happy, just in general... and it fuckin sucks biiiiiiiiig dick... i hate everything it seems... woohoo... how wonderous! NOT... i cant deal with it anymore... i cant deal with anything anymore... i dont know how to deal with it! its so much... and just... aahhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhh... i just wanna fucking scream as loud as i can into a pillow right now... and not stop EVER. wow... shoot me in the face and get it over with... more later... jflkjva;lsdjnalkscmlkj;

i dont know how im doing it... because my mom is a bitch and likes to ruin my life... i cant talk to the love of my life monday-thursday... i fucking hate it here... i just wanna leave! but on the bright side of thingssssss... friday was 2 months!!!!!!! im soooo happyyyyyyyyy... and so in love... i would/will spend the rest of my life with this boy... hes the best thing thats ever happened to my life... im just so happy! but ive been crying harder than ever for the past few hours... just because i miss him so much and cause i love him so much! i know im sound all obsessive, but i cant help it... hes just so great and so perfect... well besides the fact that i cant stop crying... im gonna go sleep...

woooooooowwwwwwwwwwww... i have so much energy right now... its definalty weird because an hour ago i was half dead! hahahahahaha so today was a pretty good day... didnt wanna be at school but i gotta deal... i gotta go to spanish class! i miss jon... he came abck for the weekend but hes going back tomorrow i think... :'( i love him so much... i hate that hes so far away... it sucks! but i gotta go... practice time... ill write more laterrrrrrr

i dont think ive cried this much or this hard in a really long time... i was on the phone with jon for about 3 or 3 1/2 hours today... he told me that hes not moving next weekend, but in the morning... i hurt more than i could describe... he broke up with me too... i wish he wasnt leaving... then none of this would be happening... i was praying that i was just having a nightmare, but i knew it was real. ive been crying since this morning... i got off the phone with him and cried in the shower, i was crying well i was getting ready, i tried REALLY hard not to cry in the car on the way to dayville which didnt work that well, i cried during Ladder 49, i cried in the car on the way home, i cried on my mommys shoulder, and im still crying... if its possible to lose weight because of crying, i totally did it... but besides all this, my day was alright... kinda boring... i did go and see Ladder 49 which was AMAZING. i was so impressed with how good it was... but i dunno... ill probably be back later tonight...

my weekend has gotten SO MUCH better... me and jon worked everything out. i love him so much, hes simply amazing! i spent a few hours talking with him on saturday morning, then i got to go to the soccer games for homecoming! the girls lost, but the boys kicked ass (undefeated 7-0)!! then me and my friends went home and had movie night and ate food. we tend to do that a lot! today has without a doubt been one of the best days ever! i spend like, 2 1/2 hours on the phone with jon well i was at jenns house and it was AMAZING! i love him so much... hearing him say my name and telling me he loved me is the best feeling in the world... its so undescribable. well maybe ill write more later... jonathan i love you!

i dont think ive ever felt as bad as i do now... me and jon for in a HUGE fight yesterday. i dont even know what i did... but whatever it was made him bitch me out worse than anyone ever has... i was so scared. i should hate him right now and i shouldnt want to be with him... but the fact of the matter is... i love him and i do want to be with him, which probably isnt good, but i cant help it... i dont want a life without jon! i went to a dance at my school last night, it was homecoming(which means nothing because we dont have a football team) so it was just like any other dance... jon was supposed to go, but he didnt... i actually did want him there because i wanted to look at him and tell him how much i love him and how much he truly has hurt me... but i was so scared at what he would do and/or say to me. he said some shit he shouldnt have and i gave up on being nice and i yelled back... i didnt know what to do... i was sobbing... but ill write more later or something... i still feel horrible

wow... this has been one hell of a day... does everyone like the new design for my LJ? my  bestest friend did it! shes so talented... i juss love her! haha thanks liv! yup... school was boring... we had "academic convacation" today... talk about a waste of time... and then i had to work at the cheerleading table thing for my lunch... what fun! haha not really... but ill survive... and tomorrow really will be a good day, i hope! im getting out of class at 12 for the pep rally and then we have the bonfire and the homecoming dance that night... jon i love you... i truly and honestly love you...

hey everyone... whats up?! how was everyones day? mine was good... had to walk home from school with manda becuase shes dumb and misses her bus! this is my first live journal... had a blurty before, bad idea. soo... my name is Cara and im 15, turning 16 in march!!!! which means ill have my lisence by june cause im starting drivers ed in february!! im excited if ya cant tell! ah yes, for those of you who always have to ask the question... im taken! im in love with the BEST guy in the world and his name is Jonathan. ive never been so happy in my life... hes incredible... the perfect guy! so sorry guys, but nothing and no one is getting me from him... lol! i had my last day of cheerleading practice today before we have the pep rally on friday... im so excited! wellll i hope you all have a sence of who i am! till later... 
    <3 always - Cara
